  <group>
    <text xml:id="originaleTedesco" xml:lang="de-AT">
      <pb xml:id="BH_194_1r"/>
      <div xml:id="1r">
        <opener hand="PW">
          <addrLine>
            <persName ref="#Beethoven">
              <roleName type="honorific"><choice><abbr type="suspension title">H</abbr><expan>Herrn.</expan></choice></roleName>
              <nameLink>Van</nameLink>
              <surname>Bethoven</surname>
            </persName>
          </addrLine>
          <salute>Schazbahrester Herr!</salute>
        </opener>
        <p hand="PW">Die <orgName ref="#MWWG">musikalische Wittwen und Waisen Gesellschaft</orgName> gibt sich die Ehre, Ihnen beyliegend mit einem freyen Billet zu allen künftigen Akademien aufzuwarten; Sie belieben solches jedesmal nur vorzuzeigen, und wieder zu behalten.</p>
        <p hand="PW">Verzeihen Sie, daß die Sozietaet, der die Versorgung ihrer Wittwen und Waisen am Herzen liegt, nicht anders, als eben so für Dero ihr bereits erwiesene Dienste, sich dankbahr zeigen kann: Nehmen Sie dieses als ihren guten Willen an, und sind Sie so gütig die Wittwen und Waisen der Sozietaet auch ins <choice><sic>künfige</sic><corr cert="high" resp="#AC">künftige</corr></choice> durch Ihre Vortrefliche Talente unterstützen zu wollen.</p>
        <closer>
          <salute hand="PW">Ewig bleibt Ihnen Verpflichtet</salute>
          <signed hand="PW">
            Die <orgName ref="#MWWG">musikalische Wittwen <lb/>und Waisen Gesellschaft</orgName>
          </signed>
          <p hand="PW">
            <foreign xml:lang="la">Ex <abbr type="suspension">concl.</abbr> Sessionis <lb/>de dato <date when="1797-01-20"><abbr type="superscription">20<sup>mo</sup></abbr> Januarij <lb/>797</date>.</foreign>
          </p>
          <dateline hand="PW">
            <placeName ref="#Vienna">Wien</placeName> <date when="1797-02-10"><choice><abbr type="suspension">d</abbr> <expan>den</expan></choice> <abbr type="superscription">10<sup>ten</sup></abbr> Februar <lb/><abbr type="acronym">a.c.</abbr></date>
          </dateline>
          <signed hand="#AS">
            <person>
              <persName ref="#Salieri">
                <forename><abbr type="suspension">Ant.</abbr></forename>
                <surname>Salieri</surname>
              </persName>
              <occupation><choice><abbr type="acronym">m.d.c.</abbr><expan>maestro di cappella</expan></choice></occupation>
            </person>
          </signed>
          <signed hand="PW">
            <person>
              <persName ref="#Wranitzky">
                <forename>Paul</forename>
                <surname>Wranizky</surname>
              </persName>
              <lb/>derzeit <occupation>Sekretär</occupation> <abbr type="suspension">derselb.</abbr>
            </person>
          </signed>
        </closer>
      </div>
      <pb xml:id="BH_194_2v"/>
      <div xml:id="2v">
        <p>An <persName ref="#Beethoven"><roleName type="honorific">Herrn</roleName> <nameLink>Van</nameLink> <surname>Betthoven</surname></persName>.</p>
      </div>
    </text>

    <text xml:id="traduzioneItaliana" xml:lang="it" corresp="#originaleTedesco">
      <pb corresp="#BH_194_1r"/>
      <div corresp="#1r">
        <opener hand="PW">
          <addrLine>
            Al <persName>
              <roleName type="honorific">Signor</roleName>
              <nameLink>Van</nameLink>
              <surname>Bethoven</surname>
            </persName>
          </addrLine>
          <salute>Stimatissimo Signore!</salute>
        </opener>
        <p hand="PW">La <orgName>Società musicale delle vedove e degli orfani</orgName> si onora di riservarLe un biglietto gratuito, accluso alla presente, per tutte le future accademie; Le piaccia solo di presentarlo ogni volta e di conservarlo.</p>
        <p hand="PW">Perdoni se la Società, che ha a cuore la cura delle vedove e degli orfani, non può mostrare in altro modo  la propria gratitudine per i servizi che già Le avete reso: voglia accettare questa come una prova della sua buona volontà ed essere così gentile da sostenere ancora in futuro le vedove e gli orfani della Società con i Suoi preziosi talenti.</p>
        <closer>
          <salute hand="PW">Sempre obbligata</salute>
          <signed hand="PW">
            La <orgName>Società musicale delle vedove e degli orfani</orgName>
          </signed>
          <p hand="PW">
            <foreign xml:lang="la">Ex <abbr type="suspension">concl.</abbr> Sessionis <lb/>de dato <date when="1797-01-20"><abbr type="superscription">20<sup>mo</sup></abbr> Januarij <lb/>797</date>.</foreign>
          </p>
          <dateline hand="PW">
            <placeName ref="#Vienna">Vienna</placeName> <date when="1797-02-10">il 10 febbraio <lb/><abbr type="acronym">a. c.</abbr></date>
          </dateline>
          <signed hand="#AS">
            <person>
              <persName ref="#Salieri">
                <forename><abbr type="suspension">Ant.</abbr></forename>
                <surname>Salieri</surname>
              </persName>
              <occupation><choice><abbr type="acronym">m.d.c.</abbr><expan>maestro di cappella</expan></choice></occupation>
            </person>
          </signed>
          <signed hand="PW">
            <person>
              <persName ref="#Wranitzky">
                <forename>Paul</forename>
                <surname>Wranizky</surname>
              </persName>
              <lb/>attuale <occupation>Segretario</occupation> <abbr type="suspension">della med.</abbr>
            </person>
          </signed>
        </closer>
      </div>
